		{ heading: `It's free to read and hear, for yourself`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — so you can listen and weigh it for yourself, in your own time, with an open and honest heart.` },
